g.text: General:Interrupt = ( FIFO fills through SRI == CHx_INTR_CFG.DINQUANT ) AND ( filled FIFO entries <= CHx_INTR_CFG.DINLVL )Example:Interrupt = ( FIFO fills through SRI == 4 ) AND ( filled FIFO entries <= 4 )
